:

1. *Zabavno* je družiti se s prijateljima. (It's fun to hang out with friends.) 
2. On je *zabavno* čovek. (He is a fun person.) 
3. Imali smo *zabavno* veče. (We had a fun night.)
4. Oni su uvek u potrazi za *zabavnim* stvarima. (They're always looking for fun things.) 
5. *Zabavno* je provesti vreme sa porodicom. (It's fun to spend time with family.)